OL,3,CCould the UK look to the Channel
OL,4,CIslands for healthier school dinners?
OL,6,FFor example, in Guernsey:
OL,8,FGuernsey schools have taken it upon
OL,9,Fthemselves to go one step further, as
OL,10,Fno deep-fried food has been served to
OL,11,Fchildren since 2011.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Jersey's School Food
OL,14,FStandards ban deep-fried foods
OL,15,Fentirely and provide guidance to their
OL,16,Fcatering partners on the use of sweet
OL,17,Fand sugary products.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
