OL,3,CCould the UK look to the Channel
OL,4,CIslands for healthier school dinners?
OL,6,FLizzie Watson, Assistant Principal of
OL,7,FInclusion at St Sampsons High School,
OL,8,Fsays providing healthy eating options
OL,9,Fis a priority.
OL,11,FShe explains: "We are trying to offer
OL,12,Fas many options to the students as
OL,13,Fpossible, and there's a lot more
OL,14,Femphasis today on healthy eating.
OL,16,F"Whether that's vegetarian, vegan or
OL,17,Fgluten-free options, or just trying to
OL,18,Fincrease students' vegetable and meat
OL,19,Fintake throughout the day, so they've
OL,20,Fgot more protein and more energy."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
