PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776442271
OL,3,CCould the UK look to the Channel
OL,4,CIslands for healthier school dinners?
OL,6,FIt is something the school has worked
OL,7,Fon in collaboration with its pupils.
OL,9,FLizzie adds: "At the end of last year,
OL,10,Fwe tried some new menu items to see if
OL,11,Fthey'd be successful with students -
OL,12,Fand we had about a hundred who taste-
OL,13,Ftested some of the healthy food
OL,14,Foptions."
OL,16,FKat Tyrell, from the island's Health
OL,17,FImprovement Commission, says they meet
OL,18,Fregularly with school caterers to
OL,19,Fensure standards are being met.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
