CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776442271
OL,3,CCould the UK look to the Channel
OL,4,CIslands for healthier school dinners?
OL,6,FShe states: "Obviously healthy food
OL,7,Fisn't always the easiest or cheapest
OL,8,Foption.
OL,10,F"It's about navigating those broader
OL,11,Fsystem issues so that children and
OL,12,Fyoung people are getting the most
OL,13,Fnutritious food they can."
OL,15,FJersey-based nutritionist Kit Chamier
OL,16,Fadds that schools are the breeding
OL,17,Fgrounds for wider cultural change.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
