PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776442271
OL,3,CCould the UK look to the Channel
OL,4,CIslands for healthier school dinners?
OL,6,FHe explains: "Ultimately, we're
OL,7,Ffeeding the next generation and if
OL,8,Fthey have that foundation of good
OL,9,Fnutrition, there will be many health
OL,10,Fbenefits they and therefore the island
OL,11,Fwill have as well."
OL,13,FHe adds that Jersey's small population
OL,14,Fmeans the island could be seen as a
OL,15,Ftest case for understanding how
OL,16,Fteaching children to care about
OL,17,Fnutrition at a young age will create
OL,18,Fgenerational change over time.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
